## RBAC — matriz de transições

| De | Para | Quem |
|---|---|---|
| *(POST /v1/receivables)* | `created` | `seller` (cria o rascunho) |
| `created` | `under_review` | `seller` (submete o formulário) |
| `under_review` | `offer` | `risk_analyst` ou `risk_analyst_agent` |
| `under_review` | `reproved` | `risk_analyst` ou `risk_analyst_agent` |
| `offer` | `approved` | `seller` (aceita a proposta) |
| `offer` | `rejected` | `seller` (recusa a proposta) |
| `approved` | `confirmed` | `payer` via magic link (`payer_magic_link` actor kind) |
| `approved` | `payer_rejected` | `payer` via magic link (`payer_magic_link` actor kind) |
| `confirmed` | `processing` | **sistema** (`X-Dupply-Api-Key` only) |
| `processing` | `completed` | **sistema** (`X-Dupply-Api-Key` only) |
| `completed` | `payer_settled` | **sistema** (`X-Dupply-Api-Key` only) |
| `completed` | `overdue` | **sistema** (`X-Dupply-Api-Key` only) |
| `overdue` | `payer_settled` | **sistema** (`X-Dupply-Api-Key` only) |

